REINFORCEMENT LEARNING WITH RELOADED SKILLS,0.16129032258064516,"Once learned, we propose two methods to transfer the hierarchical skill space to downstream tasks.
Following previous work (e.g. (Merel et al., 2019; Singh et al., 2021)), we freeze the low-level
controller p(at | zt, xt), and learn a policy for either the continuous (zt) or discrete (yt) latent."
REINFORCEMENT LEARNING WITH RELOADED SKILLS,0.16487455197132617,"Categorical agent
One simple and effective technique is to additionally freeze the mid-level com-
ponents q(zt | yt, xt), and learn a categorical high-level controller π(yt | xt) for the downstream
task. The learning objective is given by:"
